LIVING IN THE MADONNA MOMENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Calendar's Feb. 6 article on Madonna's efforts to become the first pop artist 
to sing in China was way off base. 
</P>
<P>
Troy Cory was not only the first American pop singer to be featured and perform 
at concerts in China, but was the first American singer to perform live on its 
television network. 
