<HEADLINE>
<P>
CUBAN TOURISM UP 13% 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By LEE SIEGEL and 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
From ReutersHavana 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
About 225,000 foreign tourists visited Cuba last year, a 13% rise from 1987, 
according to National Tourist Board figures published Friday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
