<DOCID> 35761 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 26, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Opinion; Part 5; Page 1; Column 4; Opinion Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
1218 words 
</P>
