<HEADLINE>
<P>
EDUCATIONAL TOURING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Every year about this time the Mature Traveler column tells us what community 
tours offers for the summer in the way of overseas professor-led tours. So far 
I have been on four. They are wonderful tours and I plan on my fifth this 
summer -- the one to the Soviet Union. We have great socials and lectures 
before we leave and those reunions after the tours are really a lot of fun. I 
have made many friends from all parts of the United States through these trips 
and I thank you for the information. 
</P>
</TEXT>
