<HEADLINE>
<P>
DELICIOUS APPLE FARM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
We stayed at the Apple Farm Inn &amp; Restaurant, 2015 Monterey St., San Luis 
Obispo 93401, phone (805) 255-2040, as a result of Jerry Hulse's recommendation 
in "The Heart's Hideaways" (Feb. 12) and it was everything Hulse said it was . 
. . and more! Very charming, spotless, friendly and beautifully decorated. And 
delicious! It was our favorite spot for a three-day getaway. I'm keeping the 
whole page of "The Heart's Hideaways." Thank you so much for this story. 
</P>
<P>
MR. and MRS. DON SHEARING 
</P>
<P>
Rolling Hills Estates 
</P>
