WASHINGTON DC; DRUG TRAFFICKING -- WASHINGTON DC; DRUG TRAFFICKING -- LOS 
ANGELES; COCAINE; CRIME STATISTICS; FEUDS; DRUG SALES; POVERTY 
</P>
