<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA032689-0131 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 35954 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 26, 1989, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
