bomb. PETER SOREL; Photo, "Steel Magnolias" cast: front, Sally Field; second 
row left, Olympia Dukakis, Julia Roberts, Dolly Parton; back row left, Daryl 
Hannah and Shirley MacLaine. ; Photo, Robert De Niro and Jane Fonda in MGM's 
