to catch a train bound east from Los Angeles. STEPHEN VAUGHAN; Photo, But 
they're actually at the Santa Ana Regional Transportation Center, right on a 
normal commute day. MANDO GONZALES / L.A. Times; Photo, Hoffman later got a hug 
from an extra at the station, below. 
</P>
